---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About GoinAtlas"
  description="GoinAtlas is a travel guide built for curious, independent travelers. We cover destinations in depth — from first-timers guides to month-by-month seasonal advice."
>
  <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6" style="font-family: var(--font-display);">About GoinAtlas</h1>

    <p class="text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] mb-6 leading-relaxed">
      GoinAtlas is a travel guide built for curious, independent travelers. We publish in-depth guides covering destinations across Asia, Europe, the Americas, and beyond — from first-timer overviews to granular advice on specific cities, neighborhoods, and months of the year.
    </p>

    <p class="text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] mb-6 leading-relaxed">
      Our content focuses on what actually matters when you're planning a trip: when to go, where to stay, how to get around, what to eat, and how much it costs. We write for travelers who want accurate, practical information — not generic tourist filler.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-10 mb-4" style="font-family: var(--font-display);">What we cover</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] space-y-2 mb-6">
      <li>Destination overviews and first-timers guides</li>
      <li>Month-by-month seasonal advice for every major destination</li>
      <li>City and neighborhood deep dives</li>
      <li>Itineraries (3 days to 3 weeks)</li>
      <li>Food, transport, budget, and practical guides</li>
      <li>Niche experiences: temples, markets, hiking, nightlife</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-10 mb-4" style="font-family: var(--font-display);">Transparency</h2>
    <p class="text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] mb-4 leading-relaxed">
      Some links on GoinAtlas are affiliate links. If you book a flight or hotel through one of our links, we may earn a small commission at no extra cost to you. This helps us keep the site running and the content free.
    </p>
    <p class="text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] mb-6 leading-relaxed">
      Affiliate relationships never influence our editorial recommendations. We link to services we'd use ourselves.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-10 mb-4" style="font-family: var(--font-display);">Contact</h2>
    <p class="text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] mb-2 leading-relaxed">
      Questions, corrections, or partnership inquiries:
    </p>
    <a
      href="mailto:hello@goinatlas.com"
      class="text-[var(--color-brand-600)] font-semibold hover:underline"
    >
      hello@goinatlas.com
    </a>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
